---
layout: base.njk
title: "Contact Brian Hafner | AI Visibility Consultant"
description: "Get in touch with Brian Hafner about AI Visibility consulting, GEO implementation, or attribution work for your service business."
---
<section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:0;">
    <div class="wrap" style="max-width:640px;">
      <h1>Let's talk about how AI sees your brand.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap" style="max-width:640px;">
      <div class="card">
        <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/contact/thank-you/">
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact">
          <p class="honeypot-field"><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field"></label></p>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="c-name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="c-name" name="name" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="c-email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="c-email" name="email" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="c-url">Company URL</label>
            <input type="url" id="c-url" name="company_url" required placeholder="https://">
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label>Which service interests you?</label>
            <div class="radio-group">
              <label class="radio-option"><input type="radio" name="service" value="Snapshot" id="svc-snapshot"> Snapshot</label>
              <label class="radio-option"><input type="radio" name="service" value="GEO Retainer" id="svc-geo"> GEO Retainer</label>
              <label class="radio-option"><input type="radio" name="service" value="Lead-to-Revenue Tracking" id="svc-attribution"> Lead-to-Revenue Tracking</label>
              <label class="radio-option"><input type="radio" name="service" value="Not sure" id="svc-unsure"> Not sure</label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="c-prompt">What prompted this?</label>
            <textarea id="c-prompt" name="prompt" required placeholder="A sentence or two on what's going on and what you're hoping to fix."></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Send</button>
          <p class="form-note">By submitting this form, you agree to receive the requested information and occasional emails from Brian Hafner. You may unsubscribe at any time. See our <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:24px; text-align:center;">
        <a href="mailto:bh@brianhafner.com">bh@brianhafner.com</a> · Based in San Diego, CA
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-cream">
    <div class="wrap" style="max-width:640px;">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How quickly do you respond?</h3>
        <p>Within 1–2 business days.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you take small projects?</h3>
        <p>Yes — the free AI Visibility Snapshot is a low-friction way to start, regardless of size.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What if I'm not sure which service I need?</h3>
        <p>Select "Not sure" above and describe what's going on — that's enough to start the conversation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://brianhafner.com/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Contact", "item": "https://brianhafner.com/contact/" }
  ]
}
</script>
